{"tid":916924,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我決定咗要去投訴便利店個收銀","createTime":"2018-11-26T04:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T16:52:22.000Z","uid":103325,"like":62,"dislike":1653,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"0496822dc82f7a723bc76d87c02df74cc44eb538","tid":916924,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:45:54.000Z","msg":"頭盔咗先：唔係投訴撚<br />\n<br />\n話説尋晚落雨，我拎住把遮去樓下間便利店買兩罐啤酒，俾錢個陣，個收銀隨手咁攞個膠袋出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：收銀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔駛膠袋啦，同埋八達通呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：留意返餘額，下一位<br />\n我響度望住個收銀，等咗幾秒，佢終於開口，但佢竟然係西晒口面咁講咗一句：下一位<br />\n<br />\n為咗海入面嘅龜龜，你對我西口西面我可以忍辱負重，但當時出面落緊大雨，我一手拎住遮仲要拎住兩罐啤酒，你竟然一句：「多謝支持環保」都無？<br />\n我自問唔係個 D 沽名釣譽嘅環保撚，唔會為一句多謝而去用少 D 膠袋，但其實佢只要講一句多謝，就可以令更多嘅人一齊支持環保，亦可以令班環保撚自我感覺良好並繼續支持環保，點解佢連行多一步，做多少少都唔肯？"},{"pid":"445aa58177786c100756c85bed8343a324d3e290","tid":916924,"uid":201309,"like":331,"dislike":5,"score":326,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"多謝支持環保"},{"pid":"4a4942e4920282330ffad6a786b1cca834c5f720","tid":916924,"uid":53227,"like":324,"dislike":1,"score":323,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:48:05.000Z","msg":"樓主出一次街咪好唔得閒"},{"pid":"d039c87594326378681a5b3d5d9e958a010bfc15","tid":916924,"uid":140604,"like":118,"dislike":7,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"樓主好型 好支持環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36f5e17e29ec000a339b2dae11d5a03a2497f66","tid":916924,"uid":103325,"like":3,"dislike":190,"score":-187,"quote":{"pid":"445aa58177786c100756c85bed8343a324d3e290","tid":916924,"uid":201309,"like":331,"dislike":5,"score":326,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T04:47:48.000Z","msg":"多謝支持環保"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime"